NK041(di)026:0: gdon bgegs 'byung po'i gsur bsngo rkyen ngan kun grol bzhugs so //
NK041(di)026:1: phye mar sha khrag sogs zas dam rdzas myong grol yod na cung zad bsres na bzang /
NK041(di)026:3: sna gang 'dzom mer bsreg chab bran la /
NK041(di)026:4: rang spyan ras gzigs su bsgom nas dmigs yul rnams la snying rje drag tu bskyed de /
NK041(di)026:6: na mahsarba ta th+aa ga ta sogs /
NK041(di)026:7: sam b+ha ra bdun dang mtshan bzhi brjod pas /
NK041(di)026:8: dmigs yul rnams kyi ci 'dod pa'i longs spyod 'dzad med bde ba chen por byin gyis brlabs la /
NK041(di)026:9: ho gsur mchod 'dod yon drug ldan pa //
NK041(di)026:10: rang rang yid la gang 'dod sprin //
NK041(di)026:11: gnam sa bar snang kun khyab cing //
NK041(di)026:13: rigs drug snying rje'i mgron rnams dang //
NK041(di)026:14: khyad par phyogs 'dir rgyu ba yi //
NK041(di)026:15: bgegs rigs lan chags sha mkhon can //
NK041(di)026:16: za 'dre shi gshed gre pho mo //
NK041(di)026:17: nad bdag rims bdag god kha'i bdag /
NK041(di)026:21: phrag dog sdang ba'i bsam pa yis //
NK041(di)026:22: gnod pa rtsom pa'i rigs kun dang //
NK041(di)026:23: dri za srid pa bar ma'i 'gro //
NK041(di)026:24: ltogs 'gong bse rags yi dwags rigs //
NK041(di)026:25: srid par las kyi dbang song bas //
NK041(di)026:26: sna tshogs gzug can kun tu rgyu //
NK041(di)026:27: sna tshogs zas can yongs tshol can //
NK041(di)026:28: bsam sbyor sna tshogs mi 'dra ba //
NK041(di)026:29: gnod pa sna tshogs kun tu spyod //
NK041(di)026:30: dbang chen dbang chung sna tshogs pa'i //
NK041(di)026:31: gdon bgegs 'byung po thams cad la //
NK041(di)026:32: pham rgyal phyogs lhung med pa yin //
NK041(di)026:33: 'dod dgu mi zad gter du bsngo //
NK041(di)026:34: yid la ci 'dod thob gyur nas //
NK041(di)026:35: gnod 'tshe gdug rtsub kun zhi zhing //
NK041(di)026:36: byang chub sems dang ldan gyur cig /
NK041(di)026:37: srog la rlom zhing bla la 'jab //
NK041(di)026:38: nor la rngam zhing zas la rku //
NK041(di)026:39: dpal la gnod pa'i 'byung po rnams //
NK041(di)026:40: mchod sbyin 'di yis tshim gyur cig /
NK041(di)026:41: tshe rabs lan chags byang gyur cig /
NK041(di)026:42: sha 'khon sdig sgrib dag gyur cig /
NK041(di)026:43: sdug bsngal nyon mongs zhi gyur cig /
NK041(di)026:44: bdag gi mchod sbyin 'di bsngosa pas //
NK041(di)026:45: 'byung po'i tshogs kun tshim gyur nas //
NK041(di)026:46: bdag dang sems can thams cad kun //
NK041(di)026:47: dus min 'chi dang nad la sogs //
NK041(di)026:48: 'gal rkyen kun dang bral gyur cig /
NK041(di)026:49: re zhing chags rnams gtan du tshim //
NK041(di)026:50: lus gdon gnas gdon la sogs grol //
NK041(di)026:51: 'dod don bar chad ma lus zhi //
NK041(di)026:52: bkra shis bde legs phun tshogs shog /
NK041(di)026:53: mnyam nyid byang chub sems kyi mthus //
NK041(di)026:54: gnod bya gnod byed thams cad kun //
NK041(di)026:55: chos dbyings bde ba chen pa'i ngang //
NK041(di)026:56: dbyer med sangs rgyas thob par shog /
NK041(di)026:57: thams cad nam mkha' mdzod bzhin du //
NK041(di)026:58: longs spyod chad pa med par shog /
NK041(di)026:59: rtsod pa med cing 'tshe med par //
NK041(di)026:60: rang dbang du na spyod par shog /
NK041(di)026:61: zag med 'dod yon drug ldan la //
NK041(di)026:62: zhen med tshul du longs spyod nas //
NK041(di)026:63: bdag med mnyam pa'i don rtogs te //
NK041(di)026:64: skye med chos sku 'thob par shog /
NK041(di)026:65: bdag gi bsod nams stobs dag dang //
NK041(di)026:66: rnam snang mngon byang las so //
NK041(di)026:67: de bzhin gshegs pa'i byin stobs dang //
NK041(di)026:68: chos kyi dbyings kyi stobs kyis su //
NK041(di)026:69: sems can rnams la phan 'dogs pas //
NK041(di)026:70: don rnams gang dag bsam pa kun //
NK041(di)026:72: de dag thams cad ci rigs par //
NK041(di)026:73: thogs pa med par 'byung gyur cig /
NK041(di)026:75: gu ru rin po che'i gsungs /
NK041(di)026:80: zhes byas la dmigs 'dun de dang ma bral ba'i ngang nas /
NK041(di)026:82: ma ni brgya tsam bgrangs nas /
NK041(di)026:83: sbyin mdo las gsungs pa'i tshigs bcad do //
NK041(di)026:84: pa rgya chen gyur pa 'di yis mthus //
NK041(di)026:85: 'gro ba'i nang nas rang byung sangs rgyas shog /
NK041(di)026:86: sngon tshe rgyal ba rnams kyis ma bsgral ba'i //
NK041(di)026:87: skye dgu 'di dag sbyin pas sgrol gyur cig /
NK041(di)026:89: 'byung po gang dag 'dir ni sogs dang /
NK041(di)026:90: bgegs rigs stong phrag brgya cu zhi sogs bkra shis kyi tshigs bcad brjod par bya'o //
NK041(di)026:91: 'di ni sbyin pa'i phar phyin rdzogs pa dang bar
NK041(di)026:92: chad zhi ba'i thabs khyad par can yin pas sus
NK041(di)026:93: kyang nyams su blang bar bya la /
NK041(di)026:94: lhag par dus ngan gyii sems can rnams brnab sems
NK041(di)026:95: dang bskam chags 'phel ba'i skabs su za 'dre 'gong
NK041(di)026:96: po mang zhing mi phyugs la 'tshe ba dang /
NK041(di)026:97: longs spyod la gnod pa mang ba'i dus dang /
NK041(di)026:98: zas nor gyi phyir yul sna tshogs su rgyu ba'i skabs dang /
NK041(di)026:99: nad rims phyugs god mang zhing rmi lam ngan pa'i skabs dang /
NK041(di)026:100: gcan spyang byi ba sogs kyis gnod pa dang /
NK041(di)026:101: 'dres gnod dang 'dre dogs che ba'i skabs sogs su byas na bar chad dang gnod pa zhi /
NK041(di)026:102: rgyun dang skabs su snying rjes kun nas bslang te byas na 'chi ba bslu /
NK041(di)026:106: tshogs rdzogs pa sogs rang gzhan la 'phral dang yun
NK041(di)026:107: gyi phan pa'i dgos pa dus ma yod pa ni
NK041(di)026:108: smros ma dgos pas nan tan bya'o //
NK041(di)026:109: ces pa'ang rgya stod dbang phug tu rmi lam rkyen
NK041(di)026:110: las phyi nang zla ba bcu pa'i tshes bco brgyad
NK041(di)026:111: la mi pham pas phan sems kyis bris pa dge
NK041(di)026:114: glud gtor 'dod yon drug ldan 'di zhes kha bsgyur la bsngo bar bya'o //
